text: Wirsberg is a municipality in Kulmbach in Bavaria in Germany. ==City arrangement== Wirsberg is arranged in the following boroughs: * Birkenhof * Cottenau * Einöde * Goldene Adlerhütte * Neufang * Osserich * Schlackenmühle * Sessenreuth * Weißenbach * Wirsberg ==References== Category:Kulmbach (district)
